269
00:15:33,166 --> 00:15:34,135
But

270
00:15:36,838 --> 00:15:39,206
Shu Yi and me.

271
00:15:39,840 --> 00:15:40,841
The three of us...

272
00:15:40,841 --> 00:15:42,176
