274
00:15:45,613 --> 00:15:46,313
Shu Yi.

275
00:15:46,313 --> 00:15:47,415
Why are you here?

276
00:15:48,215 --> 00:15:49,883
Great!

277
00:15:49,883 --> 00:15:52,120
