Shu Yi, I didn't know...

285
00:16:04,998 --> 00:16:07,435
I'm relieved now that you're the one.

286
00:16:08,836 --> 00:16:10,605
I'd like to celebrate for you.

287
00:16:10,605 --> 00:16:12,006
How about tonight?

288
00:16:12,840 --> 00:16:13,908
-Shu Yi.
-Tonight,

289
00:16:14,608 --> 00:16:15,310
eight o'clock.

290
00:16:16,210 --> 00:16:17,745
-Shu Yi.
-I'll see you then.

291
00:16:20,115 --> 00:16:21,248
Why is he in a hurry?

292
00:16:21,983 --> 00:16:23,050
Is Shu Yi

293
00:16:23,451 --> 00:16:24,518
OK?

294
00:16:58,251 --> 00:16:59,386
What are you doing?

295
00:16:59,386 --> 00:17:00,988
It's dangerous running down the stairs!

296
00:17:02,556 --> 00:17:03,358
Are you OK?

297
00:18:28,710 --> 00:18:30,578
Why Zheng Wen?

298
00:18:34,648 --> 00:18:36,751
Why choose him instead of me?

299
00:18:41,221 --> 00:18:42,656
Zheng Wen is an idiot.

300
00:18:44,791 --> 00:18:45,960
Yu Xin is a fool!

301
00:18:49,896 --> 00:18:51,866
Both of you are idiots!

302
00:18:54,268 --> 00:18:55,736
I tried so hard.

303
00:18:59,506 --> 00:19:01,341
Why do you do this to me?

304
00:19:31,673 --> 00:19:34,108
You said it was a custom-made lucky necklace.

305
00:19:43,016 --> 00:19:44,618
Not lucky at all!

306
00:22:04,220 --> 00:22:06,226
(Next episode)

307
00:22:06,226 --> 00:22:08,195
Did you know how you look just now?

308
00:22:08,195 --> 00:22:08,963
Do you want them to find out

309
00:22:08,963 --> 00:22:10,365
that you love Jiang Yu Xin?

310
00:22:11,131 --> 00:22:12,433
Recently,

311
00:22:12,433 --> 00:22:13,801
I need a page boy.

312
00:22:14,468 --> 00:22:15,470
You take the job.

313
00:22:15,470 --> 00:22:16,671
You have to be on-call

314
00:22:16,671 --> 00:22:17,805
and obey me

315
00:22:17,805 --> 00:22:19,040
until we graduate.

316
00:22:19,540 --> 00:22:20,508
No way!

317
00:22:20,508 --> 00:22:21,676
Wait and see.

318
00:22:21,676 --> 00:22:23,578
I'll defeat you hard.

319
00:22:23,570 --> 00:22:25,738
♪Only half of it will do♪

320
00:22:26,232 --> 00:22:28,397
♪I don't understand why love♪

321
00:22:28,397 --> 00:22:30,270
♪is always replaced by reality♪

322
00:22:30,669 --> 00:22:36,510
♪I'm waiting at the place
where you left, like a fool♪

323
00:22:36,980 --> 00:22:42,938
♪I never expect♪

324
00:22:43,389 --> 00:22:48,350
♪that letting go is more painful than a breakup♪

325
00:22:48,350 --> 00:22:51,614
♪You're getting further away from me♪

326
00:22:51,610 --> 00:22:54,116
♪Yet I still treasure you in my heart♪

327
00:22:54,110 --> 00:22:56,690
♪I've said goodbye to you♪

328
00:22:56,690 --> 00:23:02,431
♪But I never want you to leave♪

329
00:23:05,920 --> 00:23:11,156
♪Forgive me for never knowing♪

330
00:23:11,607 --> 00:23:17,250
♪that letting go is more painful than a breakup♪

331
00:23:17,250 --> 00:23:19,585
♪I will no longer be the reason♪

332
00:23:19,580 --> 00:23:22,240
♪for you to be happy or sad♪

333
00:23:22,240 --> 00:23:24,916
♪I've said goodbye to you♪

334
00:23:24,910 --> 00:23:31,026
♪But I'm desperate to make you stay♪
